fc\u30e0\u304c\u5909\u308f\u308b\u30b9\u30d4\u30f3\u30e2\u30fc\u30c9\u30fb\u30b9\u30d1\u30a4\u30e9\u30eb\u30e2\u30fc\u30c9\u304c\u904a\u3079\u307e\u3059\n\u2022 \u30d5\u30a3\u30c3\u30c8\u30cd\u30b9\u30fb\u30b9\u30de\u30fc\u30c8\u30a6\u30a9\u30c3\u30c1\u3067\u30ab\u30ed\u30ea\u30fc\u3092\u6d88\u8cbb\u3057\u3088\u3046\n\n\u201c\u4eca\u307e\u3067\u30d7\u30ec\u30a4\u3057\u305f\u4e2d\u3067\u3001\u6700\u3082\u5b8c\u74a7\u306b\u8fd1\u3044\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0\u201d\n10/10 - Pure PlayStation\n\n\u201c\u5168\u8eab\u3092\u4f7f\u3063\u305f\u9a5a\u304d\u306e\u4f53\u9a13\u201d\n- VR Fitness Insider\n\nBARBIE\u2122 and any associated trademarks  and trade dress are owned by, and under license from, Mattel. \u00a92024 Mattel.", "short_description": "\u30b7\u30f3\u30bb\u30e9\u30a4\u30c0\u30fc\u30ba(Synth Riders)\u306f\u3001\u97f3\u697d\u3067\u3042\u306a\u305f\u81ea\u8eab\u3092\u52d5\u304b\u3059\u30c0\u30f3\u30b9\uff06\u30ea\u30ba\u30e0\u30a2\u30af\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0\uff01\u516c\u5f0f\u30ab\u30b9\u30bf\u30e0\u66f2\u304c\u5c0e\u5165\u3055\u308c\u3066\u3044\u3066\u3001\u30de\u30eb\u30c1\u30d7\u30ec\u30a4\u30e4\u30fc\u306e\u30b3\u30df\u30e5\u30cb\u30c6\u30a3\u3082\u5145\u5b9f\u3057\u3066\u3044\u307e\u3059\uff01"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "1069919651291500", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Synth Riders", "keywords": ["Musique", "Rythme", "Danse", "Fitness", "Beat"], "long_description": "Laissez-vous emporter par la musique dans Synth Riders, un jeu d'action, de danse et de rythme \u00e0 la communaut\u00e9 grandissante, et avec la possibilit\u00e9 d'inclure ses propres chansons !\n\n\u2022 Dansez sur le rythme de 75 chansons aux genres vari\u00e9s\n\u2022 Profitez d'une prise en charge officielle des chansons personnalis\u00e9es\n\u2022 D\u00e9couvrez des DLC vari\u00e9s (Gorillaz, Bruno Mars, Muse, The Offspring, Caravan Palace, et bien d'autres)\n\u2022 Faites des sessions \u00e0 10 gr\u00e2ce au multijoueur multiplateforme\n\u2022 Vivez une exp\u00e9rience unique pour chaque chanson gr\u00e2ce aux modes rotation et spirale\n\u2022 Br\u00fblez des calories avec une montre intelligente de fitness.\n\n\u00ab De tous les jeux auxquels j'ai jou\u00e9, c'est celui qui approche le plus la perfection. \u00bb\n10/10 - Pure PlayStation\n\n\u00ab Une exp\u00e9rience physique absolument incroyable qui fait bouger tout le corps. \u00bb\n- VR Fitness Insider\n\nBARBIE\u2122 and any associated trademarks  and trade dress are owned by, and under license from, Mattel. \u00a92024 Mattel.", "short_description": "Laissez-vous emporter par la musique dans Synth Riders, un jeu d'action, de danse et de rythme \u00e0 la communaut\u00e9 grandissante, et avec la possibilit\u00e9 d'inclure ses propres chansons !"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "1048700823700930", "locale": "es_LA", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Synth Riders", "keywords": ["M\u00fasica", "Ritmo", "Futurista", "Ejercicio", "Beat"], "long_description": "\u00a1Deja que la m\u00fasica te gu\u00ede en Synth Riders, un juego de acci\u00f3n y baile r\u00edtmico con soporte oficial para canciones personalizadas y una comunidad en l\u00ednea cada vez m\u00e1s grande!\n\n\u2022 Baila al ritmo de 75 canciones de diversos g\u00e9neros.\n\u2022 Disfruta del soporte oficial para canciones personalizadas.\n\u2022 Descubre DLCs de Gorillaz, Bruno Mars, Muse, The Offspring, Caravan Palace y muchas bandas m\u00e1s.\n\u2022 Juega con 10 amigos gracias al modo multijugador interplataforma.\n\u2022 Sorpr\u00e9ndete con los modos Giro y Espiral de cada canci\u00f3n: cambiar\u00e1n la manera en la que juegas.\n\u2022 Quema calor\u00edas con un reloj inteligente con puls\u00f3metro.\n\n\u00abLo m\u00e1s cercano que he visto a un videojuego perfecto\u00bb.\n10/10 - Pure PlayStation\n\n\u00abUna experiencia f\u00edsica impresionante que involucra todo el cuerpo\u00bb.\n- VR Fitness Insider\n\nBARBIE\u2122 and any associated trademarks  and trade dress are owned by, and under license from, Mattel. \u00a92024 Mattel.", "short_description": "\u00a1Deja que la m\u00fasica te gu\u00ede en Synth Riders, un juego de acci\u00f3n y baile r\u00edtmico con soporte oficial para canciones personalizadas y una comunidad en l\u00ednea cada vez m\u00e1s grande!"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "588618373689783", "locale": "de_DE", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Synth Riders", "keywords": ["Musik", "Rhythmus", "Beat", "Tanzen", "Fitness"], "long_description": "Genie\u00dfe die anregende Musik in Synth Riders, einem Action-Tanz-Rhythmus-Spiel mit offizieller Unterst\u00fctzung f\u00fcr eigene Songs und einer st\u00e4ndig wachsenden Multiplayer-Community!\n\n\u2022 Tanze zu 75 Songs aus verschiedenen Genres\n\u2022 Viel Vergn\u00fcgen mit der Unterst\u00fctzung f\u00fcr eigene Songs\n\u2022 Entdecke DLC-Songs von K\u00fcnstlern wie Gorillaz, Bruno Mars, Muse, The Offspring, Caravan Palace und mehr\n\u2022 Triff bis zu 10 Freunde im plattform\u00fcbergreifenden Multiplayer\n\u2022 Erlebe in jedem Song die bahnbrechenden Modi \u201eSpin\u201c und \u201eSpiral\u201c\n\u2022 Verbrenne mit einer Fitness-Smartwatch \u00fcbersch\u00fcssige Kalorien.\n\n\u201eDas so ziemlich perfekteste Videospiel, das ich je gespielt habe.\u201c\n10/10 - Pure PlayStation\n\n\u201eEine aufregende Erfahrung f\u00fcr den ganzen K\u00f6rper.\u201c\n- VR Fitness Insider\n\nBARBIE\u2122 and any associated trademarks  and trade dress are owned by, and under license from, Mattel. \u00a92024 Mattel.", "short_description": "Genie\u00dfe die anregende Musik in Synth Riders, einem Action-Tanz-Rhythmus-Spiel mit offizieller Unterst\u00fctzung f\u00fcr eigene Songs und einer st\u00e4ndig wachsenden Multiplayer-Community!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://synthridersvr.com/privacy-policy",